by the actual fighting.

487
00:22:25,291 --> 00:22:26,916
Hey guys, this isn't
the right road!

488
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,833
Did you input the wrong route?

489
00:22:28,916 --> 00:22:30,583
Hey, what's going on?

490
00:22:30,666 --> 00:22:32,208
