496
00:22:48,375 --> 00:22:50,125
[PRISON GUARD T]
Hey! Don't be stupid!

497
00:22:50,208 --> 00:22:51,291
Give me the gun!

498
00:22:51,375 --> 00:22:53,833
[grunting]

499
00:22:53,916 --> 00:22:55,250
[gasps]

500
00:22:55,333 --> 00:22:56,125
Ha!

