00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,041
[DOKUFU]
Don't worry.

505
00:24:52,125 --> 00:24:54,041
We're confident that one
day we're going to see lots

506
00:24:54,125 --> 00:24:56,583
of little children
running around here!

507
00:24:56,666 --> 00:24:58,666
[gasps]

508
00:24:58,750 --> 00:25:01,750
[DOKUFU laughs]
Make your mind up!

509
00:25:01,833 --> 00:25:02,958
Time's up.

510
00:25:05,166 --> 00:25:07,666
[LAFIEL]
Kill you? Don't make me laugh!

511
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:10,416
Death would be far too
sympathetic a fate!

